# Testing Conventions

## Running Tests

```bash
./vendor/bin/pest                                    # All tests
./vendor/bin/pest --testsuite="Admin Feature Test"   # Specific suite
./vendor/bin/pest --filter="test_name"               # Specific test
```

## Test Structure

- Use `describe()` blocks to group related tests
- Use `it('can do something')` for test names
- Use `beforeEach(fn() => $this->loginAsAdmin())` for admin tests
- Use factories for test data creation
- Assert database state with `assertDatabaseHas()`/`assertDatabaseMissing()`

## API Tests

- Use `$this->getAuthenticationHeaders()` for OAuth headers
- Assert JSON structure with `assertJsonStructure()`
- Test all HTTP status codes (200, 201, 204, 403, 404, 422)
